@510  = ~It is rather unlikely, isn't it? My parents were certainly never overly religious. But I always had a strong reverence for Lathander, though, and felt his presence in my life moreso than any of the other gods my family worshipped. My mother worshipped Lathander especially, though, so maybe that isn't so strange.~
@511  = ~Shortly before I joined the order, I found that with Lathander's power moving through me, I could do things other young people my age could not.~
